Edited July 10, 2023 by SpaceNerd221

According to the error screen, several parts of 3m and 6m size have issues with nodes.  My guess is that these parts are in one of your mods and are corrupted or not available/applicable.  Which mod i cannot say.  Best bet is to uninstall all mods and then reinstall some of them to try and isolate which mod is giving you the issue.

Sans that, a copy of the log file might be helpful.
